@node "Notes" "Important notes"
@{b}@{u}IMPORTANT NOTES : PLEASE READ AT LEAST THIS !@{ub}@{uu}

1. To install Shock, just cd into Shock's directory and 
   execute install.script. This will copy contents of directories 
   libs and fonts to be added to your SYS:Libs and SYS:Fonts

2. The program requires the @{b}ORIGINAL version of the mathtrans.library@{ub}
   (you can find it in the packet), so, if you have any other, you 
   will have to copy it in your Sys:Libs directory !!   

3. You MUST copy the three fonts you find in the drawer 'Sys:FONTS'. 
   If the editor can't find theese fonts, it will refuse to load !!!

4. @{b}There is a demo@{ub} file and some pictures in a drawer. The first 
   is an already build Slide-Show (just to show what @{"Shock" link "Player" 0} can do), 
   and the others are it's components (Just open a new CLI, set on 
   Shock drawer and type : Shock Demo).

5. If yoy have any problem, send @{"me" link "About" 0} a message (address is in the docs).


Have a good shock !

 Vittorio Ferrari
@endnode

